{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~ejw/authoring/www6/sld019.htm", "content": "\r\n<!--  Presentation generated by Internet Assistant for Microsoft PowerPoint 97 -->\r\n\r\n<HTML>\r\n<HEAD>\r\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Context-Type\" CONTEXT=\"text/html;charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Microsoft Internet Assistant for Microsoft PowerPoint 97\">\r\n <TITLE>Locking Principles</TITLE> \r\n</HEAD>\r\n\r\n<BODY     >\r\n\r\n<CENTER>\r\n<TABLE WIDTH=100%> \r\n     <TR> <TD WIDTH=100% ALIGN=CENTER>\r\n         <IMG SRC=\"img019.JPG\" usemap=\"#Objmap\" WIDTH=480 HEIGHT=360 BORDER=0>\r\n     </TD> </TR>\r\n     <TR> <TD WIDTH=100% ALIGN=CENTER>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld001.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"first.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"First\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld018.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"prev.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Previous\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld020.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"next.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Next\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld034.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"last.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Last\"></A>\r\n         <IMG SRC=\"space.gif\" BORDER=0>\r\n         <A HREF=\"index.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"info.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Index\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"tsld019.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"text.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Text\"></A>\r\n     </TD> </TR>\r\n</TABLE>\r\n<P>Slide 19 of 34</P>\r\n</CENTER>\r\n<!-- <UL>\r\n<H2>Locking Principles</H2>\r\n<BR></UL></P>\r\n<P><UL>\r\n<H2>Independence of locks.  It must be possible to lock a resource without re-reading the resource.\r\n</H2>\r\n<BR></UL><UL>\r\n<H2>Multi-resource locking. It must be possible to take out a lock on multiple resources in the same action, and this locking operation must be atomic across these resources.\r\n</H2>\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n<H2>Partial resource locking.  It must be possible to take out a lock on a subsection of a resource.</H2>\r\n</UL></P>\r\n<P>  -->\r\n</Body>\r\n</HTML>\r\n", "encoding": "ascii"}